<br>
In preperation for the coming raid into HATE, I'll now post details.<br>
<br>
Port up to HATE will occur in Southern Ro, at the Wizard Portal.  I've chosen Ro as port up location becasue of it relative safety for gathering (no guards and such) and is accessable by both Wizards and Druids for ports.  Please if you are planning on coming, be in Southern Ro at 4:45 pm PST.  <br>
<br>
Loot will be handled by the raid leader or whom the raid leader designates, whom will distribute it all as it comes in.  There will be an equal roll for all items that drop for those classes that can use them.  We will attempt to distribute drops as evenly as possible.  All drops will be announced as they are looted and transphered to the Master Looter or Raid Leader, whom then will announce what dropped call for people to give tells if they are the proper class and will do a /random roll.  Will then hand over item then and there.  As of this moment there is no reserve system in place, and we don't plan on holding anything or reserving anything.  That said this raid is dependent on the cooperation of High Level volunteers, some of which may play key roles for the raid.  As such they may be interested in rogue drops (for example), and such drops may be subject to collection as opposed to distribution.  So there may be some setting aside, to get the necessary ports up to Hate and a CoH Mage which is also planned.<br>
<br>
There will be no distribution of money drops, as this is a hosted raid, money drops will be used to offset the cost of port up gems.<br>
<br>
Raid:  Subject to Cancelation WARNING!  This raid is subject to immediate cancelation if we cannot find the necessary numbers or class/levels for it.  Currently, we lack (1) a High Level Enchanter, (2) a CoH Mage, (3) Experienced Hate puller (Gore may take this slot), and (4) a Wizard for the port ups.  Lacking any one of these REQUIRED personel, we will immediately cancel the raid rather then risk a wipe out during the breakin.<br>
<br>
I cannot adequately plan groups, with so many people not posting their intent to come.  So I will simply post those who have said they expect to come to Hate.<br>
