<br>
If it turns out the raid is canceled, I will post another raid for next Wednesday, and we will try Hate again.  I've not contacted other guilds, other then Resolution and Fire and Fury, in my general call for help.  I will do so for the next event, and ask other guilds specifically.  Obviously Ancient Way is interested in serious Planes Raiding, and there certainly are other guilds that are just as interested.  So will court other guilds for next Wednesday.....April 17th, same bat time, same bat channel.  As a side note if I don't show up for that one, its becasue my Traffic Court appointment for that morning didn't go well 8( so wish me luck.<br>
